trans-unit.source: Provides extension methods for the <xref href="System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive"></xref> and <xref href="System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry"></xref> classes.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder metoder for utvidelsen for den <xref href="System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive"> </xref> og <xref href="System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry"> </xref> klasser.

trans-unit.source: The ZipFileExtensions class contains only static methods that extend the <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive> and <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry> classes.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ZipFileExtensions inneholder bare statisk metoder som utvide den <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>og <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry>klasser.</xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>

trans-unit.source: You do not create an instance of the ZipFileExtensions class; instead, you use these methods from instances of <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive> or <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry>.
trans-unit.target: Du opprette ikke en forekomst av klassen ZipFileExtensions; du bruker disse metodene fra forekomster av <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>eller <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry>.</xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>

trans-unit.source: To use the extension methods, you must reference the `System.IO.Compression.FileSystem` assembly in your project.
trans-unit.target: Du må referere til å bruke metodene utvidelse av `System.IO.Compression.FileSystem` samlingen i prosjektet.

trans-unit.source: The `System.IO.Compression.FileSystem` assembly is not available in [!INCLUDE[win8_appname_long](~/add/includes/win8-appname-long-md.md)] apps.
trans-unit.target: Den `System.IO.Compression.FileSystem` samlingen er ikke tilgjengelig i [!INCLUDE[win8_appname_long](~/add/includes/win8-appname-long-md.md)] apper.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, the ZipFileExtensions and <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFile> classes (both of which are in the `System.IO.Compression.FileSystem` assembly) are not available in [!INCLUDE[win8_appname_long](~/add/includes/win8-appname-long-md.md)] apps.
trans-unit.target: Derfor ZipFileExtensions og <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFile>klasser (begge er i den `System.IO.Compression.FileSystem` samling) er ikke tilgjengelige i [!INCLUDE[win8_appname_long](~/add/includes/win8-appname-long-md.md)] apper.</xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFile>

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[win8_appname_long](~/add/includes/win8-appname-long-md.md)] apps, you work with compressed files by using the methods in <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>, <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry>, <xref:System.IO.Compression.DeflateStream>, and <xref:System.IO.Compression.GZipStream>.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[win8_appname_long](~/add/includes/win8-appname-long-md.md)] apper du arbeider med komprimerte filer ved hjelp av metodene i <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>, <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry>, <xref:System.IO.Compression.DeflateStream>, og <xref:System.IO.Compression.GZipStream>.</xref:System.IO.Compression.GZipStream> </xref:System.IO.Compression.DeflateStream> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>

trans-unit.source: The ZipFileExtensions class contains three methods that extend <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>: - <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.CreateEntryFromFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29> - <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.CreateEntryFromFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.IO.Compression.CompressionLevel%29> - <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToDirectory%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%29> The ZipFileExtensions class contains two methods that extend <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry>: - <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%29> - <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29>
trans-unit.target: Klassen ZipFileExtensions inneholder tre metoder som utvide <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>:- <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.CreateEntryFromFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29>- <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.CreateEntryFromFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.IO.Compression.CompressionLevel%29>- <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToDirectory%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%29>for ZipFileExtensions klassen inneholder to måter som utvider <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry>:- <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%29>- <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29></xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%29> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToDirectory%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%29> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.CreateEntryFromFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.IO.Compression.CompressionLevel%29> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.CreateEntryFromFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29> </xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchive>

trans-unit.source: Archives a file by compressing it and adding it to the zip archive.
trans-unit.target: Arkiverer en fil av komprimering den og legge den til zip-arkivet.

trans-unit.source: The new entry in the archive contains the contents of the file specified by `sourceFileName`.
trans-unit.target: Den nye oppføringen i arkivet viser innholdet i filen fra `sourceFileName`.

trans-unit.source: If an entry with the specified name (`entryName`) already exists in the archive, a second entry is created with an identical name.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en oppføring med det angitte navnet (`entryName`) finnes allerede i arkivet, andre blir opprettet en oppføring med samme navn.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry.LastWriteTime%2A> property of the entry is set to the last time the file on the file system was changed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry.LastWriteTime%2A>for settes til sist ble endret filen på filsystemet.</xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry.LastWriteTime%2A>

trans-unit.source: Extracts all the files in the zip archive to a directory on the file system.
trans-unit.target: Trekker ut alle filer i zip-arkivet til en mappe på filsystemet.

trans-unit.source: This method creates the directory specified by `destinationDirectoryName`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden, oppretter katalogen som angis av `destinationDirectoryName`.

trans-unit.source: If the destination directory already exists, this method does not overwrite it; it throws an <xref:System.IO.IOException> exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis målmappen finnes allerede, denne metoden kan ikke skrive over den. Det oppstår en <xref:System.IO.IOException>unntak.</xref:System.IO.IOException>

trans-unit.source: The method also creates subdirectories that reflect the hierarchy in the zip archive.
trans-unit.target: Metoden oppretter også undermapper som gjenspeiler hierarkiet i zip-arkivet.

trans-unit.source: If an error occurs during extraction, the archive remains partially extracted.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det oppstår en feil under uttrekking, forblir arkivet delvis utpakkede.

trans-unit.source: Each extracted file has the same relative path to the directory specified by `destinationDirectoryName` as its source entry has to the root of the archive.
trans-unit.target: Hver utpakkede filen har samme relativ bane til mappen som er angitt av `destinationDirectoryName` som kilden posten har til roten av arkivet.

trans-unit.source: Extracts an entry in the zip archive to a file.
trans-unit.target: Trekker ut en oppføring i zip-arkivet til en fil.

trans-unit.source: If the destination file already exists, this method does not overwrite it; it throws an <xref:System.IO.IOException> exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis målfilen finnes allerede, denne metoden kan ikke skrive over den. Det oppstår en <xref:System.IO.IOException>unntak.</xref:System.IO.IOException>

trans-unit.source: To overwrite an existing file, use the <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29> method overload instead.
trans-unit.target: For å skrive over en eksisterende fil, kan du bruke den <xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29>metoden overbelaste i stedet.</xref:System.IO.Compression.ZipFileExtensions.ExtractToFile%28System.IO.Compression.ZipArchiveEntry%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29>
